high_descs: Go to the trash can that is behind the counter.
Remove the tomato from the trash can.
Bring the tomato to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge.
Go to the microwave to your left.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Move to the trash can on the left of the yellow chair.
Pick up the tomato from the trash can.
Bring the tomato to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge for 7 seconds.
Bring the tomato to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the door then turn right.
Pick up the tomato from the black container.
Turn right and walk to the fridge so you are in front of it facing it.
Chill the tomato in the fridge for a while before retrieving it and closing the doors.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold tomato in the microwave.
